name: Universe #280
description: Universe #280 - Gisuphus had pools of data, activated with the electric currents beneath it's wolds surfaces. They crackled and traveled through the universe, powering everything and making it run. A magnetic pulse from a nearby universe disturbed it all. The electricity became unstable and started destroying the pools. Gisuphus, gained consciousness in the process and cried in pain. 280 saw all this happening and went to the core of the universe. It pushed all the electricity out and saved the universe. Now the electricity travels in trajectory of 280 as it powers the universe. The consciousness of the universe and 280 merged.
